{"tid":315549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西藏連日暴雨　整幢樓倒塌墮河掀巨浪","createTime":"2017-07-10T06:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T07:42:14.000Z","uid":48582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9eb45c51c12643659afd32f52be79463953f3a","tid":315549,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170710/photo/bkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001_01b.jpg?20170710124859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170710%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170710124859&h=a88e55f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因企圖偷運700噸鴉片導致被港警通緝，而棄保潛逃至台灣入獄一年，及後多次要求港府撤銷控罪以求落葉歸根未果，以致終身未能回港，最終客死異鄉的馬惜珍所創立的東方日報報導，西藏昌都市連日大雨，<del>部分時段和地區甚至下暴雨，導致</del>河水猛漲。<del>其中，</del>上周六（8日）在災情較嚴重的江達縣，一幢5層高的大樓因地基被洪水掏空而突然倒塌，<del>場面恐怖。所幸事發前當局已提前疏散了大樓內的居民，</del>才未有造成人命傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n從網傳短片顯示，該幢在河邊的大樓瞬間倒塌，在河中掀起巨浪，附近民眾目睹後不禁大聲驚呼。此外，一輛停放在河邊的大貨車，亦因河岸被洪水沖塌而墮進洪水中，所幸當時車上無人。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，江達縣從6月開始持續下雨，近幾天更是出現強降雨，多處道路損毀行車中斷，至周一（10日）降雨始停。目前，從江達縣到昌都市區的國道317已經搶通，但全縣仍有共57.8公里、67條農村公路被沖毀，24座橋樑受損。強降雨還導致部分電線杆損毀，部分鄉村停電，電力仍在搶修中。<br />\n<br />\n<del>面對災情，昌都市委、市政府高度重視，要求卡若區、江達、類烏齊第一時間組織全縣幹部職工、駐地部隊、群眾開展抗洪搶險工作，對沿河居住的居民和有地質災害隱患地帶的人員第一時間進行疏散安置，保證群眾和住戶的人身安全。同時，當局又安排部署各鄉（鎮）展開洪水監測和地質災害排查工作，對出現的災害第一時間展開自救工作。</del> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170710/bkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170710%2Fbkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001.html&d=X%2By74uZZfd73voHFVcoF49Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=53d57be4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170710/bkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"484e9f6618683c4dab4088ea5c683db081cfd3e2","tid":315549,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170710/photo/bkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001_03b.jpg?20170710124859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170710%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170710112032896-0710_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20170710124859&h=71b599f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceb14f5aa2922cc87cb925005fd58eb1032d5d3e","tid":315549,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"又可以重建擦 GDP"},{"pid":"a19c5de1247ecd26df34156be93ffdf1cc25be53","tid":315549,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027c0ffbd5c9fb0979a3262f9051d73684bc21db","tid":315549,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:31:16.000Z","msg":"冇樁腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39e5df2f6b68f61dea535bcc808e45e25b51225","tid":315549,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇樁腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係下陷 緊係睇唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd402e3cb9495037a123825cf4f0edc44ae70d04","tid":315549,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"因報報導！"},{"pid":"50aa96d3a4bb29274e359c75959e02a1199c157f","tid":315549,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T07:40:38.000Z","m